channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Police on campus at Columbia and UCLA as protests disrupt colleges nationwide
item.description: Over 100 demonstrators were arrested at Columbia University and City College of New York after police cracked down on people protesting Israel's war in Gaza. Follow for live updates.

item.title: College protests updates: Protesters clash on UCLA campus, LAPD responds
item.description: Protests have broken out at colleges and universities across the country in connection with the war in Gaza.

item.title: April 30, 2024 - US university protests
item.description: Over 100 demonstrators were arrested at Columbia University and City College of New York after police cracked down on people protesting Israel's war in Gaza.

item.title: Fed expected to hold interests rates steady at highest level since 2001
item.description: The U.S. economy has faced a months-long stretch of stubborn inflation.

item.title: Ex-attorney for Daniels and McDougal testifies in Trump trial
item.description: Attorney Keith Davidson, a key witness who represented Stormy Daniels and Karen McDougal, was questioned Tuesday by prosecutors about the negotiations that led to Daniels' tabloid deal and hush money payment during the Donald Trump criminal trial.

item.title: 55 people injured after Los Angeles Metro collides with USC bus: Officials
item.description: Two people were transported to a local hospital in serious condition, according to the Los Angeles Fire Department.

item.title: April 29, 2024 - Columbia begins suspending student protesters
item.description: The deadline set by Columbia University for demonstrators to vacate an encampment there or face suspension has passed.

item.title: Student protesters reach a deal with Northwestern University that sparks criticism from all sides
item.description: An agreement between anti-war protesters and Northwestern University has largely ended demonstrations on the suburban Chicago campus

item.title: What you should know if there's no sexual attraction for your partner, according to a therapist
item.description: Why would a person pick a potential life partner without feeling the spark of sexual attraction? And can these relationships survive and thrive? Can sexual attraction be cultivated later? Therapist Ian Kerner shares what he's learned in his practice.

item.title: LIVE: ABC News Live
item.description: 24/7 coverage of breaking news and live events
